description.en: GFLOKI is an innovative AI Rebase token. AI automatically calculates the most reasonable increase and can passively reward $DOGE coins. The earlier the purchase time, the longer the token holding time, the higher the proportion of dividends. This combination of AI Rebase and Passive Dividend rewards is a new combination on the Binance Smart Chain, which will break all leaderboards!The great Musk has recently fallen in love with Genshin, and Floki is a new pet adopted by Musk.
